    "The dataset is split into training (70%) and testing (30%) sets for model evaluation.",
    "Multiple machine learning models, including DT, RF, SVM, k-NN, and ANN, have been selected for combination.",
    "Hyperparameters for each individual model have been tuned using random search to find the best set of hyperparameters within specified ranges.",
    "After tuning individual models, their predictions have been combined using stacking, a weighted averaging method.",
    "These are ensemble learning techniques used to combine predictions from multiple models."
